Aug-26 '50
Dear Jack
We will not 
be able to be in unclear on labor day
this year as our
Fall Festival starts on
labor day for 1 week.
Hope you can come
by and see us, will 
be looking for you.
Hello to all the Family
your Friends, 
Russ+Ann Weyand

Mr Jack Conroy
6012 S. Green St
Chicago, 21
Illinois

June 24
Dear Jack
Newberger also did the NY
Times review Jan 14 - (of B.P.O)
so he may syndicate. A "W.R.
Rogers: has review of it from
Maine to Texas so far - a whole
sheaf by him came in from 16
Chipping service. I hope Winkler
got a book to read, anyway.
Thank you for sending the Post-D-
Chipping. It looks good "inposition".
The chippers just sent bare review,
as you know, but this looks like a 
feature. Had mtg the 1 chopping from Service unclear
Your review pleased me very
much. I bought 20 copies to send
to friend who'll recognize your
name, as well - Thank you for
everything. Yours-Kathryn Winkler
